    <description><![CDATA[Files from Associative Indexing Service AIS - Associative Indexing Service, an application for storing bookmarks, memos, indexing of big (lifetime) archives for fast future access to the data by (personalized) keywords. In other words - it is an extension of human associative memory :) ]]></description>
